high_descs: Go across the kitchen to the white round table.
Pick up the green sponge between a red tomato and a liquid soap.
Turn around and go to the stove on the other side of the kitchen.
Place the green sponge in the gray pot on the right front burner.
Pick up the pot with the green sponge inside.
Turn around and go back to the white round table.
Place the pot with the green sponge on the table between the chair and a green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot with the green sponge on the table.

high_descs: Walk around the counter and up to the white table in the right corner of the room and stand next to the wall on the right.
Pick up the green scrub sponge sitting in front of the tomato on the right.
Turn left and walk over to the stove and stand in front of it.
On the stove, put the sponge in the right-side pot, standing upright with the yellow side facing right.
Pick up the pot with the sponge still inside.
Turn right and walk over to the white table in the corner and stand in front of the green head of lettuce.
Set the pot down on the table in front of the chair at the upper left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot, with a sponge in it, on the table.

high_descs: Go to the round white table
Pick up a sponge
Go to the stove
Put the sponge in a bowl
Pick up the bowl
Go to the round white table
Put the bowl down
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a sponge in it on a table
